{"tid":2422428,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"城巴車長車禍中身亡　受傷乘客向其遺孀及城巴索償","createTime":"2021-02-25T07:47:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T09:17:49.000Z","uid":277339,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e4ce5b9b8e82216a02a7d1070ded478052213fc6","tid":2422428,"uid":277339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:47:53.000Z","msg":"2019年3月4日西九龍快速公路西隧管制區發生2死16傷交通事故，一輛城巴直插在前方拋錨停低的密斗貨車車尾，肇事城巴車長及貨車司機雙雙不治。事隔近3年，當日城巴上一名受傷乘客入稟區域法院，向車長遺孀及城巴有限公司提出人身傷亡索償，惟入稟狀未有標明索償金額。<br />\n<br />\n原告胡新偉，兩名被告分別是肇事車長蘇國偉的遺產管理人、即蘇的遺孀譚少珍及他的女兒，以及城巴有限公司。入稟狀透露，原告是肇事城巴上的乘客，他在事件中受傷，乃由於蘇疏忽及違反謹慎責任所造成，而城巴身為蘇的僱主亦需承擔賠償責任。<br />\n<br />\nsource︰東方"},{"pid":"eb6850fe35aecbcb99c6ee99d0ed77b7c809cd27","tid":2422428,"uid":810,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:48:50.000Z","msg":"當年世界大戰 巴士佬究竟有冇恰眼訓"},{"pid":"8e435bb0f7663dbff73e3dbc008855a85dac2a80","tid":2422428,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb6850fe35aecbcb99c6ee99d0ed77b7c809cd27","tid":2422428,"uid":810,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:48:50.000Z","msg":"當年世界大戰 巴士佬究竟有冇恰眼訓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:49:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c152a5078e7766e64a455057e9705002dac27493","tid":2422428,"uid":212509,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:51:29.000Z","msg":"其實個貨車司機先係始作俑者"},{"pid":"39287bfbd19bbbc95b9031ef266ced078c2db82b","tid":2422428,"uid":190333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:52:00.000Z","msg":"三年定兩年呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a629d782c5699a9c8b88388760859712416d1c","tid":2422428,"uid":118120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"39287bfbd19b